name: r-rodbc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.3-19" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rodbc
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/RODBC_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/RODBC/RODBC_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3afcbd6877cd8b7c8df4a94bacd041a51e5ac607810acb88efd380b45d2d4efe

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [r_base == "3.6"]
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}grep              # [win]
    - {{ posix }}autoconf
    - {{ posix }}automake          # [not win]
    - {{ posix }}automake-wrapper  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}pkg-config
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - unixodbc                   # [unix]
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - unixodbc                   # [unix]

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('RODBC')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('RODBC')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=RODBC
  license: GPL-2 | GPL-3
  summary: An ODBC database interface.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - croth1
